metadata.title: Quadrangle Boundaries 1:250,000

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Alaska Department of Natural Resources, Division of Support Services-Land Records Information Section

metadata.description: Data Type: Base Maps  ;This coverage contains the boundaries of the USGS protracted 1:250,000 quadrangle maps covering Alaska. It also includes annotation for the quadrangle names in the annotation subclass qmqanno.
